text: Ashish Kumar (born 1990) is an Indian gymnast. Ashish Kumar may also refer to: * Ashish Kumar (actor), Indian actor and director * Ashish Kumar (boxer), Indian amateur boxer * Ashish Kumar Saha, Indian politician from Tripura * Ashish Kumar Singh, Indian politician from Uttar Pradesh * Ashish Kumar Louho (1937–1994), Bangladeshi actor * Ashish Kumar Chauhan, Indian business executive * Ashish Kumar Ballal, Indian field hockey player * Ashish Kumar Yadav (born 1984), Indian politician * Ashish Kumar (cricketer) (born 1988), Indian cricketer
title: Ashish Kumar (disambiguation)
